		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Depends entirely on the game, really. On some it's obvious it's just some dumb deformation, but some take the effort to make the road at a distance match the actual intended turn (it becomes especially obvious when you're going downhill and next ahead is uphill).

		

